{"word":"G2225 - ζωογονέω - zōogonéō - dzo-og-on-eh'-o - Live","slug":"G2225","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ζωογονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>zōogonéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dzo-og-on-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Live"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B6;&#x03C9;&#x03BF;&#x03B3;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - zo&#x0304;ogoneo&#x0304;</b> - <i>dzo-og-on-eh'-o</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2226\">G2226</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1096\">G1096</a>; to <i>engender alive</i> that is, (by analogy) to <i>rescue</i> (passively <i>be saved</i>) from death: - live, preserve."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1186\">G1186</a>, <a href=\"#/G2198\">G2198</a>, <a href=\"#/G2222\">G2222</a>, <a href=\"#/G2226\">G2226</a>, <a href=\"#/G2227\">G2227</a>, <a href=\"#/G326\">G326</a>"}]}